      <title>芝加哥、圣地亚哥准备与特朗普边境沙皇霍曼展开斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-18/chicago-san-diego-brace-for-fight-with-trump-border-czar-homan</link>
